table.name: claim
table.description: Information for a single damage claim in GC3

columns.name: CLAIM_GID
columns.description: The GID for damage claim.

columns.name: CLAIM_XID
columns.description: The XID for the claim.

columns.name: DAMAGE_INFORMATION
columns.description: Text description of damage.

columns.name: REPORT_DATE
columns.description: Date incident is reported.

columns.name: INCIDENT_DATE
columns.description: Date incident occurred.

columns.name: DAMAGE_NOTIFY_POINT_GID
columns.description: Code for notification point for damage claim, user defined in power data.

columns.name: DAMAGE_CAUSE_GID
columns.description: Code for cause of damage, user defined in power data.

columns.name: DAMAGE_NATURE_GID
columns.description: Code for nature of damage, user defined in power data.

columns.name: DAMAGE_VALUE
columns.description: Financial loss (value) of only the damaged goods; may be calculated by the system or specified by the user.

columns.name: DAMAGE_VALUE_CURRENCY_GID
columns.description: The GID for the damage value currency.

columns.name: DAMAGE_VALUE_BASE
columns.description: Damage value in the base currency.

columns.name: IS_DAMAGE_VALUE_FIXED
columns.description: If Y, the system will not calculate damage value and will keep the value entered by user.

columns.name: SIZE_OF_LOSS
columns.description: Financial loss for the entire claim including all losses incurred and credits; may be calculated by the system or specified by the user.

columns.name: SIZE_OF_LOSS_CURRENCY_GID
columns.description: The GID for the size of loss currency.

columns.name: SIZE_OF_LOSS_BASE
columns.description: Size of loss amount in base currency.

columns.name: IS_SIZE_OF_LOSS_FIXED
columns.description: If Y, the system will not calculate size of loss and will keep the value entered by user.

columns.name: SHIPMENT_GID
columns.description: The GID of the shipment relating to the claim.

columns.name: INDICATOR
columns.description: Claim indicator value.

columns.name: USER_DEFINED1_ICON_GID
columns.description: A user-defined icon for the claim.

columns.name: USER_DEFINED2_ICON_GID
columns.description: A user-defined icon for the claim.

columns.name: USER_DEFINED3_ICON_GID
columns.description: A user-defined icon for the claim.

columns.name: USER_DEFINED4_ICON_GID
columns.description: A user-defined icon for the claim.

columns.name: USER_DEFINED5_ICON_GID
columns.description: A user-defined icon for the claim.

columns.name: NOTIFICATION_DATE
columns.description: Date of notification for the claim.

columns.name: NOTIFY_PARTY_CONTACT_GID
columns.description: Party that notified of the damage.

columns.name: LIABLE_PARTY_CONTACT_GID
columns.description: Party responsible for causing damage.

columns.name: IS_SELF_RECONDITION
columns.description: Indicates if the claim is self-reconditioning.

columns.name: DOMAIN_NAME
columns.description: Database domain where this data is stored.

columns.name: INSERT_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data insert user.

columns.name: INSERT_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data insert.

columns.name: UPDATE_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data update user.

columns.name: UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of the most recent data update.
